                     <interp inst="t18450203-493-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp> for stealing 1 coat, value 5<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; 2 pictures and frames, 3<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; 1 pair of scissors, 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.; and 1 pair of stockings, 1<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; the goods of <persName id="t18450203-name-524" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18450203-name-524" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18450203-name-524" type="surname" value="FAGAN"></interp>
