                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi> I have seen him in such a dress—I have not received any description of his dress from the pawnbroker—I knew him well—he has worn several dresses lately—I produce a certifi<lb></lb>cate of the prisoner's former conviction, which I got from Mr. Clark's</p>
